      <a href="https://t.me/game8la" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tg-join-btn">立即加入 t.me/game8la</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-disclaimer">
    <p><strong>⚠️ 免責聲明：</strong>本站為遊戲資訊評測與攻略分享平台，<strong>不提供任何博弈服務</strong>，亦不經營、代理、介紹或撮合任何線上博弈行為。所有內容僅供學術研究、產業觀察與娛樂閱讀參考之用。</p>
    <p><strong>🔞 僅限 18 歲以上成年人瀏覽。</strong>未成年人請立即離開本站。請理性看待娛樂活動，切勿沉迷；如有情緒困擾或博弈成癮問題，請撥打衛福部安心專線 <a href="tel:1925">1925</a>（24 小時免費）、生命線 <a href="tel:1995">1995</a>，或亞洲公益社 <a href="tel:0800080888">0800-080-888</a>。</p>
    <p>依據中華民國法律，任何形式之賭博行為均屬違法。本站對讀者自行連結之第三方平台所產生之任何後果不負任何責任。</p>
  </div>

  <a href="/articles/game8la-manifesto/" class="trust-badge" aria-label="Game8la 100% Independent & No Referral Links 宣言">
    <span class="tb-shield"><Icon name="shield" size="1.1rem" /></span>
    <span class="tb-text">
      <strong>100% Independent &amp; No Referral Links</strong>
      <small>Game8la 零娛樂城外鏈・零 NGR 抽成・只給真評價</small>
    </span>
    <span class="tb-arrow">看宣言 →</span>
  </a>

  <div class="footer-bottom">
    &copy; 2026 GAME8LA. All Rights Reserved. | 本站僅提供遊戲資訊評測與攻略分享。
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  /* === FOOTER === */
  .footer {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 3rem 2rem 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: calc(1.5rem + env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px));
  }

  .footer-grid {
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-col h4 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .footer-col p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-col a {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .footer-col a:hover {
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  .footer-disclaimer {
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .footer-disclaimer p { margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .footer-disclaimer strong { color: #ffb347; }
  .footer-disclaimer a {
    color: #ffd966;
    text-decoration: underline;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .trust-badge {
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(57,255,20,0.08), rgba(255,16,240,0.06));
    border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.35);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .trust-badge:hover {
    border-color: #39FF14;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(57,255,20,0.18);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .trust-badge .tb-shield {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; flex: 0 0 40px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(57,255,20,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.5);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: #39FF14;
  }
  .trust-badge .tb-text { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.15rem; line-height: 1.4; }
  .trust-badge .tb-text strong {
    color: #39FF14;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .trust-badge .tb-text small { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .trust-badge .tb-arrow {
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .footer .logo-footer {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .footer .footer-logo-img {
    height: 100px;
    width: auto;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.25));
  }

  .footer-email {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.7rem;
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .footer-email a {
    color: var(--gold-light) !important;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0 !important;
    display: inline !important;
  }
  .footer-email a:hover {
    color: #39FF14 !important;
  }

  /* === Social Row (LINE + TG) === */
  .footer-social-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .footer-social-btn {
    display: inline-flex !important;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem !important;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.82rem !important;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .footer-social-btn span {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }

  .line-btn {
    background: rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.35);
    color: #06C755 !important;
  }
  .line-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.2);
    color: #06C755 !important;
  }

  .tg-btn-inline {
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.25);
    color: var(--guava-green) !important;
  }
  .tg-btn-inline:hover {
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.15);
    color: var(--guava-green) !important;
  }

  /* === TG Group Column === */
  .footer-col-tg h4 {
    color: var(--guava-green);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .tg-sub {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .tg-qr-link {
    display: block;
    max-width: 180px;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .tg-qr-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .tg-join-btn {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.55rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(57,255,20,0.12), rgba(255,215,0,0.08));
    border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.3);
    color: var(--gold-light, #f5d78e);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .tg-join-btn:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(57,255,20,0.2);
  }

  /* === RESPONSIVE === */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .trust-badge { flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 0.9rem 1rem; }
    .trust-badge .tb-arrow { width: 100%; text-align: right; }

    .footer {
      padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
